## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="efeb8-102"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs>对象具有一个 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> 属性，该属性可分配给 <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> 事件处理程序中的长时间运行 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceView.ContextCreating> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efeb8-102">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> object has a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> property that can be assigned to a long-running <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> in the handler for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceView.ContextCreating> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="efeb8-103">有关详细信息，请参阅 [对象上下文生命周期管理 (EntityDataSource) ](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/67bc2486-112c-47c3-b23f-0297f7ac2160)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efeb8-103">For more information, see [Object Context Life-Cycle Management (EntityDataSource)](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/67bc2486-112c-47c3-b23f-0297f7ac2160).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="efeb8-104">下面的示例演示如何创建对象的 <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> 变量并将 <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> 其分配给 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> 对象的属性 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efeb8-104">The following example shows the creation of an <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> variable of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> object and its assignment to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> object.</span></span>  
  
```  
public partial class _Default : System.Web.UI.Page  
    {  
        AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities objCtx =  
            new AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities();  
  
        protected void EntityDataSource2_ContextCreating(object sender,   
            EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs e)  
        {  
            e.Context = objCtx;  
        }  
    }  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
